{
  "stem": "1550.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then the British said, well, who are you?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course they knew who we were, because the other two ships had arrived before.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Right?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they knew, but they said we are-- we are Jewish refugees from-- from Germany and other countries here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, well, all right, we'll send you on to Palestine, and you'll get some food.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But first of all, for the food you have to pay.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "See, the Greeks had supplied us with food for free.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The British, we had to pay.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, in other words, everybody-- I-- everybody had either one pound-- either-- we were allowed to take out of Germany either one pound or $5.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had, I think, one pound and my parents each had $5.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- I think some of it had to be handed over to pay for the food-- bread and other food-- that-- that we got from the British.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were very stingy, I must tell you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was-- that-- everybody was very angry about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think even some people had to hand over some of their jewelry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that I don't-- that I'm not sure about.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I remember we had to hand our-- hand over what little money we had.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And also we had a big box of German drugs that we were allowed to take.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And these are-- [INAUDIBLE] we handed that also over to the British, which was very valuable, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the British supplied us with coal and with a British crew, with a British captain, and coal, and we sailed for Palestine, which is very close from Cyprus to-- to Haifa is just a-- just a day.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we sailed for Palestine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we saw the-- the promised land [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in the distance.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
